00:08:23,467 --> 00:08:24,717
Mais um ou dois.

52
00:08:27,342 --> 00:08:28,342
Não.

53
00:08:29,717 --> 00:08:30,717
Esses.

54
00:08:33,797 --> 00:08:34,823
Um quilo.

55
00:08:34,883 --> 00:08:36,217
Seis dirhams.

56
00:08:36,383 --> 00:08:38,258
